[C]The girl in this story is Abilene Rose
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 10}
This is the story I promised to tell
[G7]All you young cowboys remember it well
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 11}
If you find true love don't tear it apart
[C]Marry that true love don't break her young heart
{end_of_verse}

